This paper discusses biases in machine learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) in computer science. Additionally, the paper also touches upon the sub-categories of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI), "Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science" (cs.CE), "Cryptography and Security" (cs.CR), and "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS) as these fields are also relevant to the topic of biases in big data.
